  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Integrate 500 patients of mental health  in Rwanda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mental illness support in Rwanda is left behind. Many of patients have no access to proper diagnosis, long term treatment, care or counseling and social integration. This project will allow NDUHURA Organization to integrate 500 of mental health patients in their social environment and advocate for their rights and raise awareness to reduce stigma through a community-based network of trained health professionals. With this help, we can change the lives of many of mentally ill patients in Rwanda.</narrative>
  </description>
